Install Postfix/Dovecot with Vpopmail interface to the MySQL backend
   1. Minimum install Springdale/Rocky/Alma Linux 8
   2. # curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/qmtoaster/posttoasty/main/install.sh --output /usr/local/bin/posttoasty
   3. # chmod 755 /usr/local/bin/posttoasty
   4. # posttoasty
   5. Additional features: https://www.linuxbabe.com/mail-server/setup-basic-postfix-mail-sever-ubuntu
Postfix utilizes Dovecot's AUTH and LMTP
